  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Cloud Specialist (Infrastructure)",
  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Cloud Specialist (Infrastructure)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Manage Cloud DevOps Infrastructure</strong></li>\n  <li>Design, propose, deploy cloud infrastructure, platform and applications. </li>\n  <li>Implement cloud infrastructure in UAT and product environment.</li>\n  <li>Manage and monitor performance, security, availability, and scalability of cloud resources.</li>\n  <li>Troubleshoot and debug issues related to cloud resources and infrastructure.</li>\n  <li>Implement security measures to protect cloud resources.</li>\n  <li>Familiar to GCC environment requirement, setup and deployment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong technical knowledge on RHEL or Windows Operating System.</li>\n  <li><strong>Strong in Cloud DevOps Infrastructure.</strong></li>\n  <li>Proficient in automation tools like AWS Lambda, Step Functions, and AWS Systems Manager</li>\n  <li>Experience in CI/CD and Infrastructure as Code tools like Gitlab, Terraform, CloudFormation and Ansible.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with scripting languages like Python, Bash, and PowerShell</li>\n  <li>3-5 years Cloud Infrastructure working experience</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of security best practices</li>\n  <li>Possess Cloud certification (AWS /Azure /GCP/Huawei).</li>\n  <li>Knowledge in Active Directory, Public Key Infrastructure or Networking will be advantageous</li>\n  <li>Singaporean Only!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p>\n<p>Please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to : jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</p>\n<p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
